# Copy to device as: I:\config\credentials.txt
# Preferred format is salted SHA-256:
# username=sha256:<salt-hex>:<hash-hex>
#
# Tip: easiest is to let the device create/update this file via the Auth UI after first boot.
# If you must pre-provision, create a user line like below (replace values):
# admin=sha256:0123456789abcdef:fedcba9876543210
